{{Use dmy dates|date=December 2016}} {|{{Infobox ship begin}} <!-- warships except submarines --> |+Yugoslav torpedo boat ''T5'' {{Infobox ship image |Ship image=[[File:Yugoslav torpedo boat T3.jpg|300px|alt=a black and white photograph of a medium-sized ship underway]] |Ship caption= ''T5''{{'}}s sister ship, ''T3'' }} {{Infobox ship career |Hide header= |Ship country=[[Austria-Hungary]] |Ship flag={{shipboxflag|Austria-Hungary|naval}} |Ship name=''87 F'' |Ship namesake= |Ship ordered= |Ship builder=[[Ganz Works|Ganz & Danubius]] |Ship laid down=5 March 1914 |Ship launched=20 March 1915 |Ship acquired= |Ship commissioned=25 October 1915 |Ship decommissioned= |Ship in service= |Ship out of service=1918 |Ship honours= |Ship fate=Assigned to the [[Kingdom of Yugoslavia|Kingdom of Serbs, Croats and Slovenes]] |Ship notes= }} {{Infobox ship career |Hide header=title |Ship country=Kingdom of Yugoslavia |Ship flag={{shipboxflag|Kingdom of Yugoslavia|naval}} |Ship name=''T5'' |Ship namesake= |Ship acquired=March 1921 |Ship commissioned= |Ship decommissioned= |Ship in service= |Ship out of service=April 1941 |Ship honours= |Ship fate=Captured by Italy |Ship notes= }} {{Infobox ship career |Hide header=title |Ship country=Italy |Ship flag={{shipboxflag|Kingdom of Italy|naval}} |Ship name=''T5'' |Ship namesake= |Ship acquired=April 1941 |Ship in service= |Ship out of service=September 1943 |Ship honours= |Ship fate=returned to Yugoslavia |Ship status= |Ship notes= }} {{Infobox ship career |Hide header=title |Ship country=Kingdom of Yugoslavia |Ship flag={{shipboxflag|Kingdom of Yugoslavia|naval}} |Ship name=''T5'' |Ship namesake= |Ship acquired=December 1943 |Ship commissioned= |Ship decommissioned= |Ship in service= |Ship out of service=May 1945 |Ship honours= |Ship fate= |Ship notes= }} {{Infobox ship career |Hide header=title |Ship country=Yugoslavia |Ship flag={{shipboxflag|Yugoslavia|naval}} |Ship name=''Cer'' |Ship namesake= |Ship acquired=May 1945 |Ship commissioned= |